Package: ggsunburstR
Title: Sunburst and Icicle Adjacency Diagrams with ggplot2
Description: Create sunburst and icicle adjacency diagrams using ggplot2.
    Accepts hierarchical data in multiple formats (Newick strings/files,
    data frames, lineage files, node-parent files), computes rectangle
    coordinates for each node, and produces standard ggplot2 objects that
    users can customise with familiar '+' syntax. A pure-R reimplementation
    of 'ggsunburst' that eliminates the Python/reticulate dependency.
Version: 0.2.0
